SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM atlas.ods_order FINAL
WHERE dttm_utc_1_min >= toDateTime('2020-12-15 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND dttm_utc_1_min < toDateTime('2020-12-29 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND car_class
in ('econom')
AND nearest_zone in ('kaluga')

;

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM atlas.ods_order FINAL
WHERE dttm_utc_1_min >= toDateTime('2020-12-27 21:00:00', 'UTC')
AND dttm_utc_1_min < toDateTime('2020-12-28 21:00:00', 'UTC')
AND car_class
in ('econom')
AND nearest_zone in ('moscow')

;

WITH (
    SELECT round(AVG(cost), 2) FROM atlas.ods_order
    WHERE dttm_utc_1_min >= toDateTime('2020-12-15 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND dttm_utc_1_min < toDateTime('2020-12-29 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND car_class
in ('econom')
AND nearest_zone in ('kaluga')

) AS avg_cost


SELECT
    source_geopoint[1] as order_source_lon,
    source_geopoint[2] as order_source_lat,
    surge_value as surge_value,
    toDate(order_due, 'Europe/Moscow') as local_dt,
    toInt8(toMinute(order_due, 'Europe/Moscow') / 10) as ten_minutes,
    cost as order_cost,
    cost / avg_cost as cost_weight,
    (cost - COALESCE(surcharge * surge_beta, 0))
        / (COALESCE(surge_alpha, 1) * greatest(surge_value, 1.0) + COALESCE(surge_beta, 0)) as order_cost_before_surge,
    toHour(order_due, 'Europe/Moscow') as hour,
    toDayOfWeek(order_due, 'Europe/Moscow')  as dow,
    taxi_status == 'complete' and status == 'finished' and (transporting_time > 2) as subv_flag,
    cand_perf_point[1] as driver_lon,
    cand_perf_point[2] as driver_lat,
    nearest_zone as nearest_zone
FROM atlas.ods_order FINAL
WHERE dttm_utc_1_min >= toDateTime('2020-12-15 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND dttm_utc_1_min < toDateTime('2020-12-29 12:20:47', 'UTC')
AND car_class
in ('econom')
AND nearest_zone in ('kaluga')

    AND 1 = 1
;
